A '''canoe''' was a primitive watercraft. The [[Cerean/Legends|Cerean]] canoes were one-person boats used on [[Cerea/Legends|Cerea]]. [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] also used canoes. Usually in a diamond like shape, it used two paddles on each side to propel itself.

